Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Software Engineer-AI position with Disney. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack web applications, AI/ML integration, and intelligent recommendation systems, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

